- All form elements must use shadcn/ui components: `Input`, `Select`, `Textarea`, `Button`, `FormField`, `Label`, etc.
- Layout and spacing should follow TailwindCSS utility classes.
- Use `Card`, `Tabs`, `Dialog`, `Popover`, and `DropdownMenu` components where appropriate.
- Modal interactions must use `Dialog` from `@/components/ui/dialog`.
- Do not override shadcn component styles directly â€” extend via className when needed.
- All UI elements must support light/dark mode automatically.
- Component usage must be consistent across dashboards: form fields, tables, filters, etc.
